22#include "bfd.h"

25/* Print the version number and copyright information, and exit.
26 This implements the --version option for the various programs. */
27
28void
29print_version (const char *name)
30{
31 /* This output is intended to follow the GNU standards document. */
32 /* xgettext:c-format */
33 printf ("GNU %s %s\n", name, BFD_VERSION_STRING);
34 printf (_("Copyright (C) 2018 Free Software Foundation, Inc.\n"));
35 printf (_("\
36This program is free software; you may redistribute it under the terms of\n\
37the GNU General Public License version 3 or (at your option) any later version.\n\
38This program has absolutely no warranty.\n"));
39 exit (0);
40}
